电影的原创配乐由卡特·布尔维尔作曲，他已经多次与科恩兄弟合作。撰写剧本时兄弟俩已经选好了几首歌曲，像{{link-en|肯尼·罗杰斯 (歌手)|Kenny Rogers|肯尼·罗杰斯}}的《Just Dropped In (to See What Condition My Condition Was in)》、{{link-en|吉普赛国王|Gipsy Kings}}的封面版《[[加州旅馆|加州旅馆]]》，还有[[克里登斯清水复兴合唱团|克里登斯清水复兴合唱团]]的多首歌曲<ref name="Greene">{{Cite news | last = Greene | first = Andy | title = Inside the Dude's Stoner Soundtrack | work = Rolling Stone | date = 2008-09-04 | url = http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/inside-the-dudes-stoner-soundtrack-19691231 | accessdate = 2013-06-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130923224807/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/inside-the-dudes-stoner-soundtrack-19691231 | archive-date = 2013-09-23 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他们请T-本恩·本内特来为电影原声带挑选歌曲。他们知道自己想要的是不同时代不同类型的音乐作品，据乔尔的回忆，“T-本恩甚至选出了一些[[亨利·曼西尼|亨利·曼西尼]]和[[伊玛·苏玛克|伊玛·苏玛克]]（的作品）。”<ref name="Altman">{{Cite news | last = Altman | first = Billy | title = A Music Maker Happy to Be Just a Conduit | work = The New York Times | date = 2002-02-24 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2002/02/24/movies/music-a-music-maker-happy-to-be-just-a-conduit.html | accessdate = 2013-06-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130526053055/http://www.nytimes.com/2002/02/24/movies/music-a-music-maker-happy-to-be-just-a-conduit.html | archive-date = 2013-05-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>本内特成功获得了使用肯尼·罗杰斯和吉普塞国王歌曲的版权，并且增加了{{link-en|牛心上尉|Captain Beefheart}}和Moondog的曲目，也得到了[[鲍勃·迪伦|鲍勃·迪伦]]的歌曲《The Man in Me》的使用权<ref name="Greene" />。不过[[滚石乐队|滚石乐队]]歌曲《Dead Flowers》由{{link-en|汤斯·范·赞特|Townes Van Zandt}}演绎的专缉封面版则要麻烦一些，这一曲目最终在电影的片尾字幕部分使用。前滚石乐队经理人艾伦·克莱恩（{{lang|en|Allen Klein}}）拥有这首歌的版权并开价15万美元。于是本内特说服克莱恩观看电影的前期剪辑版本，他回忆道，“当演到督爷说，‘哥们，我真他妈恨死这[[老鹰乐队|老鹰乐队]]了！’克莱恩站起来说，‘够了，你可以用这首歌！’感觉真太美妙了。”<ref name="Greene"/><ref name="flowers">{{cite web |url=http://www.rollogrady.com/the-big-lebowski-dead-flowers/ |title=The Big Lebowski // Dead Flowers – Rollo & Grady: Los Angeles Music Blog |publisher=Rollogrady.com |date=2008-08-29 |accessdate=2013-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130606033346/http://www.rollogrady.com/the-big-lebowski-dead-flowers/ |archive-date=2013-06-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>本内特将在电影主创人员名单上以“音乐总监”的身份出现，但他要求把名头改为“音乐档案员”，因为本内特“恨死了做个总监这么个概念，我可不想让任何人觉得我是个什么管理人员”<ref name="Altman"/>。

对乔尔来说，“原创配乐，和电影中的其它元素，都必须呼应60和70年代的复古感”<ref name="Ciment, Michel"/>，每一个角色都有相应的音乐界定。比如科恩兄弟编写剧本时就选择了鲍勃·迪伦的《Tumbling Tumbleweeds》作为“陌生人”的主题，又如亨利·曼西尼的《Lujon》则针对的是杰基·崔霍恩一角。“那些德国虚无主义者对应的是电子风行乐，而杰夫·布里吉斯则是克里登斯（清水复兴合唱团）。所以每人都有一个音乐上的签名。”伊森在接受采访时说<ref name="Ciment, Michel" />。

==发行与专业评价==
《谋杀绿脚趾》于1998年1月18日在[[圣丹斯电影节|圣丹斯电影节]]举行了首映式，并在可以容纳1300名观众的埃克尔斯剧院发映，还参加了2月举行的第48届[[柏林国际电影节|柏林国际电影节]]<ref name="Berlinale">{{cite web |url=http://www.berlinale.de/en/archiv/jahresarchive/1998/02_programm_1998/02_Programm_1998.html |title=Berlinale: 1998 Programme |accessdate=2013-06-30 |work=berlinale.de |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BQx1CaDO?url=http://www.berlinale.de/en/archiv/jahresarchive/1998/02_programm_1998/02_Programm_1998.html |archive-date=2012-10-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Variety">{{Cite news | title = Berlinale 1998: Pix in official selection |work=Variety | date = 1998-02-09}}</ref>。3月6日影片开始在北美1207家电影院播映，首周入账550万美元，之后在美国总计收入为1700万美元，刚刚超过1500万美元的预算。电影在其他国家上映收入为2800万美元，将全球票房提高到了4618万9568美元<ref name="numbers" /><ref name="boxoffice">{{Cite news | title = ''The Big Lebowski'' | publisher = Box Office Mojo | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=biglebowski.htm | accessdate = 2013-07-01 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/612HJxQ5O?url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=biglebowski.htm | archive-date = 2011-08-18 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

许多观众和评论家把本片比作一部现代[[西部片|西部片]]，但也有许多人反对这一点，或是将之视为一部以张冠李戴式的情节来推动故事发展的犯罪小说<ref name="comentale">{{cite book |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=B_rQPB8QHawC&printsec=frontcover&dq=The+Year%27s+Work+in+Lebowski+Studies#v=onepage&q&f=false |title=The Year's Work in Lebowski Studies By Edward P. Comentale, Aaron Jaffe p.230 |accessdate=2013-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140626033632/http://books.google.com/books?id=B_rQPB8QHawC&printsec=frontcover&dq=The+Year%27s+Work+in+Lebowski+Studies#v=onepage&q&f=false |archive-date=2014-06-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。彼尔·豪威尔（{{lang|en|Peter Howell}}）发表在《[[多伦多星报|多伦多星报]]》的评论中写道，“很难相信这会是去年因《法戈》拿下[[奥斯卡最佳原著剧本奖|奥斯卡最佳原著剧本奖]]那支队伍的作品。这部电影中有大量的亵渎性言辞，看起来似乎是在无力地尝试着要填充对话间的间隙。”<ref name="Howell, Peter">{{Cite news | last = Howell | first = Peter | title = Coens' latest doesn't hold together ''The Big Lebowski'' is more sprawling than large |work=Toronto Star | date = 1998-01-19}}</ref>不过他在之后的一份评论中改变了自己的观点，表示“这可能就是我最喜欢的科恩兄弟电影”<ref name="howell">{{cite web|last=Howell|first=Peter|title=<nowiki>Howell: I love The Big Lebowski — even though the Wikipedia says I don’t</nowiki>|url=http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/2011/07/07/howell_i_love_the_big_lebowski_even_though_the_wikipedia_says_i_dont.html|work=Toronto Star|date=2011-07-07|accessdate=2013-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131227234228/http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/2011/07/07/howell_i_love_the_big_lebowski_even_though_the_wikipedia_says_i_dont.html|archive-date=2013-12-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

托德·麦卡锡（Todd McCarthy）在《[[综艺|综艺]]》杂志上写道，“电影的一个没有争议的成就就是其配乐，其中既包含卡特·布尔维尔的原创配乐，又混合有经典流行音乐和一些美妙的封面曲目”<ref name="McCarthy">{{Cite news | last = McCarthy | first = Todd | title = ''The Big Lebowski'' | work = Variety | date = 1998-01-20 | url = http://variety.com/1998/film/reviews/the-big-lebowski-1117436792/ | accessdate = 2013-07-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130813185913/http://variety.com/1998/film/reviews/the-big-lebowski-1117436792/ | archive-date = 2013-08-13 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》给予电影三星的评价（最高为四星），觉得督爷是“一个在保持（观众）兴趣上太过被动的英雄”，但电影中还是有“足够多的惊人光辉”，认为科恩兄弟还是不会让人感到失望<ref name="Wloszczyna, Susan">{{Cite news | last = Wloszczyna | first = Susan | title = ''The Big Lebowski'': Coen humor to spare |work=USA Today | date = 1998-03-06}}</ref>；

德森·霍维（{{lang|en|Desson Howe}}）发表在《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》上的评论称赞了科恩兄弟和“他们的灵感，对怪异、奇特美式风格的怪异品味——但又完全是一种新发明的美式风格——科恩兄弟已经定义了自己离奇的流派，并且成为其中的大师。没有人有相似的风格，而且几乎可以肯定地说，没有人能做得更好。”<ref name="Howe, Desson">{{Cite news | last = Howe | first = Desson | title = ''The Big Lebowski'': Rollin' a Strike |work=Washington Post | date = 1998-03-06}}</ref>

简妮特·玛丝琳（{{lang|en|Janet Maslin}}）在《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》上赞扬了布里吉斯的表演。“布里吉斯先生找到了一个看起来比以往任何一个都更适合他的角色”，认为其步履蹒跚的表演和一些看似不经意的表现发挥出了自己的喜剧天赋<ref name="Maslin, Janet">{{Cite news | last = Maslin | first = Janet | title = A Bowling Ball's-Eye View of Reality | work = The New York Times | date = 1998-03-06 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1998/03/06/movies/film-review-a-bowling-ball-s-eye-view-of-reality.html | accessdate = 2013-07-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131011105850/http://www.nytimes.com/1998/03/06/movies/film-review-a-bowling-ball-s-eye-view-of-reality.html | archive-date = 2013-10-11 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。安德鲁·萨瑞斯（{{lang|en|Andrew Sarris}}）在《[[纽约观察家|纽约观察家]]》上写道，“电影引来了许多笑声，并对其中所包含的精湛工艺产生一股敬畏之情。我怀疑今年还有其它任何一部作品有做到这一点。”<ref name="Sarris, Andrew">{{Cite news | last = Sarris | first = Andrew | title = A Cubist Coen Comedy | work = New York Observer | date = 1998-03-08 | url = http://observer.com/1998/03/a-cubist-coen-comedy-men-in-white-meet-men-with-guns-scorseses-cheat-sheet-on-american-film/ | accessdate = 2013-07-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140202154138/http://observer.com/1998/03/a-cubist-coen-comedy-men-in-white-meet-men-with-guns-scorseses-cheat-sheet-on-american-film/ | archive-date = 2014-02-02 | dead-url = no }}</ref>伊恩·内森（{{lang|en|Ian Nathan}}）对电影给出了五星的最高评价，他写道，“对于那些喜欢科恩兄弟以神圣抽象的手法来表现现实的人们来说，这（部电影）纯粹就是一个必杀技”，而且“在一个完美的世界里，所以的电影都是科恩兄弟拍的”<ref name="nathan">{{cite web|last=Nathan|first=Ian|title=Review of The Big Lebowski|publisher=Empire|date=May 1998|url=http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/reviewcomplete.asp?DVDID=117203|accessdate=2013-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110824235454/http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/reviewcomplete.asp?DVDID=117203|archive-date=2011-08-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》的[[罗杰·艾伯特|罗杰·艾伯特]]给予影片三星（最高为四星）的评价，形容这部电影有一种“古怪的魅力”<ref name="ebert">{{cite web|url=http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-big-lebowski-1998|title=The Big Lebowski|publisher=Roger Ebert|accessdate=2013-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130630160742/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-big-lebowski-1998|archive-date=2013-06-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

不过，乔纳森·罗森堡（{{lang|en|Jonathan Rosenbaum}}）在《芝加哥读者》（{{lang|en|Chicago Reader}}）上对《谋杀绿脚趾》给出了较为负面的评价，认为该片空有“炫耀性的拍摄技巧来产生很强的娱乐性”，但是其所代表的精英主义道德立场却不值得肯定<ref name="Rosenbaum, Jonathan">{{Cite news | last = Rosenbaum | first = Jonathan | title = L.A. Residential | work = Chicago Reader | date = 1998-03-06 | url = http://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/la-residential/Content?oid=895709 | accessdate = 2013-07-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130512180346/http://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/la-residential/Content?oid=895709 | archive-date = 2013-05-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。戴夫·科尔（{{lang|en|Dave Kehr}}）批评影片的故事前提让人感到厌倦，“创造出的是一部偶发性且神经质的电影”<ref name="Kehr, Dave">{{Cite news | last = Kehr | first = Dave | title = Coen Brothers' Latest is a Big Letdownski | work = Daily News | date = 1998-03-06}}</ref>。《[[卫报|卫报]]》批评本片是把“一堆点子铲进一个袋子里，然后就这么随随便便地倒出来。这部电影让人气愤，它什么奖都拿不到。不过里面还是有一些不错的笑话。”<ref name="Guardian">{{Cite news | title = Meanwhile, ''The Big Lebowski'' should have stayed in the bowling alley ... |work=The Guardian | date = 1998-04-24}}</ref>
根据[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]网站上收集的85篇专业评价文章，其中68篇给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”为80%，平均评分7.2（满分10分）<ref name="tomato">{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/big_lebowski/#!reviews=top_critics |title=The Big Lebowski Movie Reviews |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2013-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130619115102/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/big_lebowski/#!reviews=top_critics |archive-date=2013-06-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上一共收集了22篇本片的专业评价文章，其中14篇给予好评，1篇给出差评，7篇褒贬不一，平均得分69（满分100）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-big-lebowski |accessdate=2013-07-01 |title=The Big Lebowski Reviews |work=Metacritic |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131018073732/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-big-lebowski |archive-date=2013-10-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==影响==
自最初上映，《谋杀绿脚趾》就成为了一部[[邪典电影|邪典经典]]<ref name="russell">{{Cite news |last=Russell |first=Will |title=Hey Dude: The Lebowski Festival |work=The Independent |date=2007-08-15 |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/hey-dude-the-lebowski-festival-461663.html |accessdate=2010-05-13 |archivedate=2010-05-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100514042508/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/hey-dude-the-lebowski-festival-461663.html |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。史蒂夫·帕罗波利（{{lang|en|Steve Palopoli}}）曾于2002年7月在文章中提到过电影的新兴邪典地位<ref name="Palopoli, Steve">{{Cite news | last = Palopoli | first = Steve | title = The Last Cult Picture Show | publisher = Metro Santa Cruz | date = 2002-07-25 | url = http://www.metroactive.com/papers/metro/07.25.02/lebowski1-0230.html | accessdate = 2013-07-01 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/612HTC1vx?url=http://www.metroactive.com/papers/metro/07.25.02/lebowski1-0230.html | archive-date = 2011-08-18 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他是在2000年到洛杉矶的新比佛利电影院看一场午夜放映电影时意识到本片有着一定数量的邪典粉丝，当时他听到许多人交谈时彼此引述片中的台词<ref name="Green, Bill" />{{rp|129}}。他的文章发表后不久，[[圣塔克鲁兹_(加利福尼亚州)|圣塔克鲁兹]]当地午夜影院的程序员决定放映《谋杀绿脚趾》，结果仅第一个周末他们就必须谢绝数百名观众的光顾。之后剧院连续放映该片超过6个星期，这在以前从来都没有发生过<ref name="Green, Bill" />{{rp|130}}。

[[File:Moore_and_Bridges_Lebowskifest.jpg|thumb]]

2002年，[[肯塔基州|肯塔基州]]的[[路易维尔_(肯塔基州)|路易维尔]]举办了首届“勒保斯基节”（Lebowski Fest），有150名粉丝到场，并从此发展成为一个年度庆典活动，还扩张到了其它多个城市<ref name="Hoggard, Liz">{{Cite news | last = Hoggard | first = Liz | title = Get with the Dude's vibe | work = The Guardian | date = 2007-07-22 | url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2007/jul/22/features.review | accessdate = 2013-06-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100514041738/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2007/jul/22/features.review | archive-date = 2010-05-14 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。这一盛会每年最主要的活动就是一整晚不受限制的保龄球之夜，其中包含有各种各样的比赛，有根据难度的、投球距离的、自由式等等，整场年会为时超过一星期，通常在保龄球比赛前还会有配备乐队演出的聚会，以及同样有乐队演出，持续一整天的户外聚会，供应商展位、游戏也都是必不可少的内容。电影中的多位名流还出席了一些活动，如杰夫·布里吉斯就出席了在洛杉矶举行的活动<ref name="Hoggard, Liz"/>。英国也有了与勒保斯基节同样性质的庆祝活动，这一被称为信守督爷的活动在[[伦敦|伦敦]]举行<ref name="Hodgkinson, Will">{{Cite news |last=Hodgkinson |first=Will |title=Dude, let's go bowling |work=The Guardian |date=2005-05-11 |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2005/may/11/1 |accessdate=2013-06-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110503053910/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2005/may/11/1 |archivedate=2011-05-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

2005年，一种主要致力于传播本片主角督爷生活方式和处世哲学的在线宗教“督爷教”成立，也称为“当代督爷教堂”。该组织通过其网站在全世界拥有超过13万教众<ref name="Anderman, Joan">{{Cite news | last = Anderman | first = Joan | title = <nowiki>How ‘The Big Lebowski’ became a cultural touchstone and the impetus for festivals across the country</nowiki> | work = Boston Globe | date = 2009-09-15 | url = http://www.boston.com/lifestyle/articles/2009/09/15/the_big_lebowski_spawns_its_own_subculture/ | accessdate = 2013-06-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130927084922/http://www.boston.com/lifestyle/articles/2009/09/15/the_big_lebowski_spawns_its_own_subculture/ | archive-date = 2013-09-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2008年，《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》将《谋杀绿脚趾》评为过去25年中最好笑电影的第8位<ref name="ewtop25">{{Cite news |title=The Comedy 25: The Funniest Movies of the Past 25 Years |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2008-08-27 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0,,20221235_17,00.html |accessdate=2013-06-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130606081619/http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0%2C%2C20221235_17%2C00.html |archivedate=2013-06-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，同年评选的“自83年起最值得收藏的25部邪典电影”中也将本片排到第15位<ref name="EWCult25">{{Cite news | title = The Cult 25: The Essential Left-Field Movie Hits Since '83 | work = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2008-09-03 | url = http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0,,20221982_10,00.html | accessdate = 2013-07-01 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/612HdTthE?url=http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0,,20221982_10,00.html | archive-date = 2011-08-18 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2003年该杂志评选50部最佳邪典电影，本片列第34位<ref name="EWCult">{{Cite news | title = The Top 50 Cult Films | work = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2003-05-23 | url = http://www.listsofbests.com/list/63-the-top-50-cult-movies | accessdate = 2013-06-30 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130722205308/http://www.listsofbests.com/list/63-the-top-50-cult-movies | archivedate = 2013-07-22 | df =  }}</ref>。2010年，《娱乐周刊》还进行了一次“过去20年电影中最出色的100个角色”投票选举，督爷最终名列第14位<ref name="ewtop100">{{Cite news | title = The 100 Greatest Characters of the Last 20 Years |work=Entertainment Weekly | date = 2010-07-04 | page = 64}}</ref>。影片还得到了{{link-en|比利时影评人协会|Belgian Film Critics Association}}大奖提名<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://archives.lesoir.be/breves_t-19990112-Z0G80N.html|title="Hana Bi": grand prix U.C.C.|journal=Le Soir|date=1999-01-12|page=10|accessdate=2013-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130602133046/http://archives.lesoir.be/breves_t-19990112-Z0G80N.html|archive-date=2013-06-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2008年，一组《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》的作家和编辑以及两位评论家通过投票把《谋杀绿脚趾》评为过去25年所有在洛杉矶取景电影中的第10名，这个名单上每一位导演只能有一部作品上榜，他们认为这部电影体现出了洛杉矶固有的真实一面<ref name="boucher">{{Cite news | last = Boucher | first = Geoff | title = L.A.'s story is complicated, but they got it: The 25 best L.A. films of the last 25 years | work = Los Angeles Times | date = 2008-08-31 | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2008/aug/31/entertainment/ca-25films31 | accessdate = 2013-07-01 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6E7JdHKA2?url=http://articles.latimes.com/2008/aug/31/entertainment/ca-25films31 | archive-date = 2013-02-01 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在《[[帝国杂志|帝国杂志]]》进行的100个最优异的电影角色票选活动中，沃尔特名列第49位，督爷排在第7位<ref name="EmpirePoll">{{Cite news | title = The 100 Greatest Movie Characters | work = Empire | url = http://www.empireonline.com/100-greatest-movie-characters/default.asp?c=7 | accessdate = 2013-07-01 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/612HefaSd?url=http://www.empireonline.com/100-greatest-movie-characters/default.asp?c=7 | archive-date = 2011-08-18 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2010年3月，罗杰·艾伯特把《谋杀绿脚趾》列入他的“伟大电影”名单<ref name="ebert2">{{Cite news | last = Ebert | first = Roger | title = The Big Lebowski (1998) | work = Chicago Sun-Times | date = 2010-03-10 | url = http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/great-movie-the-big-lebowski-1998 | accessdate = 2013-07-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130705124246/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/great-movie-the-big-lebowski-1998 | archive-date = 2013-07-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

约翰·特托罗曾多次表示自己有意用本片中的角色接拍一部[[衍生作品|衍生电影]]。如果这个计划得到落实，科恩兄弟不会执导，但可能会参与编剧工作<ref name="Turturro AV club">{{cite web |url=http://www.avclub.com/articles/john-turturro,58178/2/ |title=Randon Roles:John Turturro |publisher=Onion AV Club |date=2011-06-28 |accessdate=2013-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130416051909/http://www.avclub.com/articles/john-turturro%2C58178/2/ |archivedate=2013-04-16 }}</ref>。此外还有一位芝加哥的滑稽模仿空想家与一家公司合作基于本片制作了一部独特且广受赞誉的滑稽模仿作品<ref name="Rollin' Outta Here Naked: A Big Lebowski Burlesque">{{Cite news | last = Hill | first = J. Scott | title = Chicago Stage Review | date = 2012-08-27 | url = http://www.chicagostagereview.com/rollin-outta-here-naked-a-big-lebowski-burlesque-tonight-only-chopin-theatre/ | accessdate = 2013-07-02 | archive-url = https://archive.is/20130702030025/http://www.chicagostagereview.com/rollin-outta-here-naked-a-big-lebowski-burlesque-tonight-only-chopin-theatre/ | archive-date = 2013-07-02 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

2019年上映的《[[復仇者聯盟：終局之戰|復仇者聯盟：終局之戰]]》中，身材發福留著長髮大鬍子的[[雷神索爾|雷神索爾]]，曾被[[東尼·史塔克_(漫威電影宇宙)|鋼鐵人]]以「Lebowski」（督爷的姓氏）開玩笑<ref>{{Cite news | last = Parker | first = Ryan | title = 'Avengers: Endgame' and That 'Big Lebowski' Homage | work = The Hollywood Reporter | date = 2019-04-26 | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/avengers-endgame-big-lebowski-homage-1204450 | accessdate = 2019-11-30 | archive-date = 2019-09-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190921155129/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/avengers-endgame-big-lebowski-homage-1204450 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

===社会和政治分析===
《谋杀绿脚趾》已经作为一种工具被用作分析多个议题。2008年9月，《{{link-en|石板 (杂志)|Slate (magazine)|石板}}》杂志发表了一篇[[历史修正主义|修正主义]]文章，将本片视为一种政治上的批判。这一观点的核心论据在于沃尔特一角是“一位[[新保守主义|新保守主义者]]”，电影意指当时的[[美国总统|美国总统]][[乔治·H·W·布什|乔治·H·W·布什]]和第一次[[海湾战争|海湾战争]]<ref name="WalterNeocon">{{Cite news | last = Haglund | first = David | title = Walter Sobchak, Neocon | date = 2008-09-11 | work = Slate Magazine | url = http://www.slate.com/articles/arts/dvdextras/2008/09/walter_sobchak_neocon.html | accessdate = 2013-07-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130321153159/http://www.slate.com/articles/arts/dvdextras/2008/09/walter_sobchak_neocon.html | archive-date = 2013-03-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

发表在女权主义杂志《暗箱》上一篇由布莱恩·沃尔（{{lang|en|Brian Wall}}）撰笔的文章用本片来解释[[卡尔·马克思|卡尔·马克思]]的[[商品拜物教|商品拜物教]]，以及[[恋物|恋物]]的女权主义后果<ref>{{cite article|author=Brian Wall |year=2008 |title=Jackie Treehorn Treats Objects Like Women!: Two Types of Fetishism in The Big Lebowski |publisher=Camera Obscura |volume=23 No. 3 |pages=111-135}}</ref>。

电影被用作对社会的一个[[嘉年华会狂欢|嘉年华会狂欢]]式批判<ref>{{cite book |author=Paul Martin |author2=Valeria Renegar |year=2007 |title="The Man for His Time" The Big Lebowski as Carnivalesque Social Critique |publisher=Communication Studies |volume=58, No. 3 |pages=299-313 |url=http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/10510970701518397#.UdThOqy-uCg |accessdate=2013-07-02}}</ref>，或是用来分析战争和伦理道德<ref>{{cite web |url=http://sub.uwpress.org/content/34/2/98.citation |title="This Aggression Will Not Stand": Myth, War, and Ethics in The Big Lebowski |publisher=Sub.uwpress.org |date=2005-01-01 |accessdate=2013-07-02 |author=Todd A. Comer |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151124055200/http://sub.uwpress.org/content/34/2/98.citation |archive-date=2015-11-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，或是对大众传播和美国[[军国主义|军国主义]]的叙述等<ref>{{cite web |url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1467-954X.2006.00641.x/full |title=Part Three Representing Automobility: No literal connection: images of mass commodification, US militarism, and the oil industry, in The Big Lebowski - Martin-Jones - 2006 - The Sociological Review - Wiley Online Library |publisher=Onlinelibrary.wiley.com |date=2006-09-18 |accessdate=2013-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140520034603/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1467-954X.2006.00641.x/full |archive-date=2014-05-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 家用媒体 ==
环球影业旗下的家庭娱乐公司于2005年10月18日发行了《谋杀绿脚趾》的[[限定版|珍藏版]][[DVD|DVD]]，其中除正片外还有一些花絮内容，包括“莫蒂默·杨所做的介绍”、“杰夫·布里吉斯画廊”、“拍摄《谋杀绿脚趾》”以及“制作笔记”。此外还有一个限量发行的“成功人士版礼品套装”，其中增加了《谋杀绿脚趾》保龄球鹿皮巾，四个印有电影剧照和引用台词的收藏品杯垫，还有8张杰夫·布里吉斯个人收藏的独家照片卡<ref name="Foster">{{Cite news | last = Foster | first = Dave | title = ''The Big Lebowski'' CE in October | publisher = DVD Times | date = 2005-08-27 | url = http://film.thedigitalfix.com/content/id/57690/the-big-lebowski-ce-in-october-artwork-added.html | accessdate = 2013-07-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140112053208/http://film.thedigitalfix.com/content/id/57690/the-big-lebowski-ce-in-october-artwork-added.html | archive-date = 2014-01-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2008年9月9日发行的“10周年版”不但包括了2005年珍藏版的全部内容，还增加了以前所发行DVD的内容如首张DVD中包含的预告片等，这一次的10周年同样有标准版和限量版两种，后者有独立的编号，而且还包括“保龄球包装”<ref name="Foster2">{{Cite news | last = Foster | first = Dave | title = ''The Big Lebowski'' 10th AE (R1) in September | publisher = DVD Times | date = 2008-04-06 | url = http://film.thedigitalfix.com/content/id/67857/the-big-lebowski-10th-ae-r1-in-september.html | accessdate = 2013-07-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120426184609/http://film.thedigitalfix.com/content/id/67857/the-big-lebowski-10th-ae-r1-in-september.html | archive-date = 2012-04-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2011年8月16日，环球影业发行了《谋杀绿脚趾》的[[蓝光影碟|蓝光影碟]]。其限量版包装包括一份杰夫·布里吉斯的相册，一个十周年的回顾，还有对从2002年起举办一年一度“勒保斯基节”的一个深入介绍<ref name="matheson">{{cite news|last=Matheson|first=Whitney|title=Cool stuff on DVD today: 'Lebowski' on Blu-ray!|url=http://content.usatoday.com/communities/popcandy/post/2011/08/cool-stuff-on-dvd-today-lebowski-on-blu-ray/1|accessdate=2013-07-01|newspaper=USA Today|date=2011-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012025949/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/popcandy/post/2011/08/cool-stuff-on-dvd-today-lebowski-on-blu-ray/1|archive-date=2012-10-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

